---
const defaultTestimonialPicture =
  'https://res.cloudinary.com/castrokev-in/image/upload/v1694376477/castrohomebuilders/reviews/default-profile-picture.png';

const testimonials = [
  {
    name: 'Ruth Stergiou',
    image:
      'https://res.cloudinary.com/castrokev-in/image/upload/v1694376447/castrohomebuilders/reviews/ruth-stergiou.webp',
    message:
      'It was a pleasure working with Victor and his team. They were conscientious, turned up when they said they would and did a great job on my project which was converting a den to a studio. I liked their attention to detail and high quality workmanship. Victor did a great job keeping everyone on track and communicating with me throughout the project.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Les Mur Des Fleurs',
    image:
      'https://res.cloudinary.com/castrokev-in/image/upload/v1694376448/castrohomebuilders/reviews/les-mur-des-fleurs.webp',
    message:
      "Castro Home Builders are licensed, efficient, and have worked with San Jose's city permits requirements routinely.  They are professional and reasonably priced.  Great workers!  We had them replace our garage rooftop, and build our work studio with half bathroom in the back of our property.  The studio has a double pane sliding walls.",
  },
  {
    name: 'Padir Consulting Engineers',
    image:
      'https://res.cloudinary.com/castrokev-in/image/upload/v1694376447/castrohomebuilders/reviews/padir-consulting-engineers.webp',
    message:
      'I know and worked with Victor as a professional. We conducted the seismic retrofit design for a project in San Jose. Victor was the contractor for that project and he did an excellent job for the project. He has a very good talent to coordinate and manage the project in different situations. He is also excellent in coordination with E.O.R. His prices are fair and I have him as our trusted contractor on our list as a Consulting engineer.',
  },
