  //   name: 'Sam',
  //   message:
  //     'Victor and his team of experts did an incredible job on our two-story addition and deck. They delivered within a very reasonable timeline and budget. Victor is a true craftsman, and the new spaces in our home came out beautifully. We are absolutely thrilled with the results, and would recommend him highly to anyone looking for a trustworthy, talented, and reliable contractor.',
  // },
  // {
  //   name: 'Leland C.',
  //   message:
  //     'Home renovation is not as easy as it looks like it is on popular tv shows, and finding the right contractor to trust is even harder. Thankfully my fiance and I got a referral to Victor and his team at Castro Home Builders. Victor had attentiveness to detail from understanding our scope of work, meeting at the site for a walkthrough, and ultimately providing a thoughtful bid.  He was always responsive via phone call, email or text. Though we decided eventually to go with another general contractor, we had them as a top contender and will plan to use them should our project turn south with our selected GC.',
  // },
  // {
  //   name: 'Liang Fang',
  //   message:
  //     'We did a major house expansion project. It was the first major house remodeling project we did.  So we had a lot of questions and decisions to make.  Victor and his team did a great deal of the project.  He was very helpful walking us through the project, answering a lot of questions with a great deal of patience.  He was knowledgeable and responsive.  He provided lots of good suggestions to help decision making.  We are very grateful for his help.',
  // },
];
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="v mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
      <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-center text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        Trusted by the Bay Area for over 20 years
      </h2>
      <div class="gap-y-6 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3">
        {
          testimonials.map((testimonial) => (
            <figure class="mx-auto flex max-w-lg flex-col items-center gap-6 py-8 lg:px-8 lg:py-0">
              <div class="flex flex-row gap-2">
                {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
                  <svg
                    class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="currentColor"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <path d="M12.0006 18.26L4.94715 22.2082L6.52248 14.2799L0.587891 8.7918L8.61493 7.84006L12.0006 0.5L15.3862 7.84006L23.4132 8.7918L17.4787 14.2799L19.054 22.2082L12.0006 18.26Z" />
                  </svg>
                ))}
              </div>
              <figcaption class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                <img
                  class="mx-auto h-8 w-8 rounded-full"
                  src={testimonial.image || defaultTestimonialPicture}
                  alt={testimonial.name}
                />
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="text-base font-medium">{testimonial.name}</div>
                </div>
              </figcaption>
              <blockquote class="text-md text-center italic leading-loose text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70">
                <p>{`“${testimonial.message}”`}</p>
              </blockquote>
            </figure>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
